XB-Plugin-Section: filesystems

Package: openmediavault-unionfilesystems
Architecture: all
Depends: mergerfs,
         openmediavault (>= 3.0.60),
         php5-cli,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Union filesystems plugin for OpenMediaVault.
 Makes it possible to mount drives under a single mountpoint with an union
 filesystem such as aufs, mhddfs and mergerfs.
